{"author":{"id":"4bb6c1767e50694cfde61856db22bf137d1651e8a0b5ca858c486db3dd02f280"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1774458077,"nonce":"FDeohn9WPozE0UEAlP0kltd40dQ=","title":"Umbrella: Part 2 analysis modules","message":"Parent issue for all Part 2 (with SISU) analysis modules.\n\nPart 2 covers analysis of networks trained with varying plant perturbation amplitude AND the SISU (sensory input signaling upcoming) contextual input. These analyses characterize how networks use SISU to modulate control strategy.\n\n## Existing modules\n- `feedback_perts`: Feedback impulse responses conditioned on SISU (profiles, aligned vars, violin measures)\n- `fps_reach`: Fixed point structure during reaching (FPs along trajectory, PCA, candidates)\n- `fps_steady`: Steady-state fixed points with Jacobian eigendecomposition, SVD of input Jacobians\n- `plant_perts`: Plant perturbation responses with SISU (tangling, aligned trajectories, profiles, measures)\n- `sisu_pert`: SISU step perturbation (change SISU mid-trial; effector trajectories, network activity, aligned vars)\n- `tangling`: PCA on hidden states during reaching, tangling computation in PC space\n- `unit_perts`: Single-unit stimulation analysis (response profiles, regression, Jacobian input channel norms)\n\n## Planned modules (no code yet)\n- Null-space decomposition of SISU effects\n- SISU sensitivity / Jacobian analysis\n- Adversary strategy verification\n\n## Child issues\nSee individual issues tagged with this umbrella ID.","files":null}]}